animeDescription: As a result of a traffic accident, Limit-chan is reborn as a cyborg and is given three types of supernatural powers. However, there is a catch: if she uses too much of them, her life will come to an end.(Source: ANN)
animeStaff: [['Oosugi, Kumiko', 'Theme Song Performance'], ['Kikuchi, Shunsuke', 'Music'], ['Komatsubara, Kazuo', 'Character Design, Animation Director'], ['Yukimuro, Shunichi', 'Screenplay']]
